{"tid":2304404,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"科大校長論壇衝突案 將於12月2日下午高等法院申請上訴期間保釋","createTime":"2020-11-28T17:57:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-29T13:08:14.000Z","uid":240362,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"5b1d458a9c8f5e0bd4c9525a5500c6671d34388a","tid":2304404,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T17:57:45.000Z","msg":"香港科技大學學生會 HKUST Students' Union:<br />\n<br />\n校長論壇衝突案早前於東區裁判法院裁決，被捕同學在證據不足的情況下依然被裁判官鄭紀航重判九個月又兩星期，更被拒絕保釋等候上訴。<br />\n<br />\n本會今午收到消息案件經申請後將會審議是否批出上訴許可，並將會由高院法官黃崇厚審理，而案件將於十二月二日（下週三）下午二時三十分於高等法院三樓第一庭進行審訊。本會呼籲有心支持被捕同學打算到場旁聽的各位可以預留位置讓親友進場。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/posts/4047978415216970\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FHKUSTSU%2Fposts%2F4047978415216970&d=7TTtdOR49HUCBqTToLMoRwwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=409fccd8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/HKUSTSU/posts/4047978415216970</a>"},{"pid":"32e7986c644a500ec745eb6afd583eafe909542f","tid":2304404,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T18:02:07.000Z","msg":"黃崇厚 好似少數正常人嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbd8ca890977b6d58d889fd23e86c0fa8b392ed9","tid":2304404,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T18:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4609a9eabdcd150bee8c6aabc6f5b7da6dd74eac","tid":2304404,"uid":114951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-28T18:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cead17976ee44c61cb34bdeab86262d2b4138716","tid":2304404,"ui